PrecisAppointment of an ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of ALBERTA, namely the Hon. RENE PAUL FOISY, who shall execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor from October 6 to October 13, 1995, during the absence, illness or other inability of the latter.
